snippet.title: The Untold Truth About Adam Lambert
snippet.description:
When Adam Lambert first auditioned for American Idol, he went all-out by singing Queen’s “Bohemian Rhapsody,” and it worked, as Lambert ended up finishing second on the Fox singing competition. However, even in his wildest dreams, Lambert couldn’t have imagined that his time on American Idol would lead to him singing for Queen on tour. It’s been a hard road to get where he is, but there’s no denying that Adam Lambert is an American Idol success story. From his struggles with his early fame to the time he was arrested in Finland, let’s take a look at the untold truth of Adam Lambert.
